unt, Netflix will offer employees a 1,890 TL monthly cash allowance to supplement the cost of an individual health plan.  When we are big enough, we will offer a group medical plan through Allianz.  If possible, we recommend getting an individual policy with Allianz to avoid completing underwriting on the group plan."},{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"ggdabL3Xy0ackC68QWsgu","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2018-10-25T21:18:14.061Z","updatedAt":"2020-12-28T21:08:47.309Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":4,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"sectionContent"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"Ext Global Section - Mental Health Support","sectionTitle":"Mental Health Support","sectionDescription":"At Netflix, we know you want to produce work you are proud of. In order to perform your best, you have to feel your best. That is why we provide unlimited coaching through Ginger; meditation and mindfulness resources through Headspace; and access to free therapy, counseling, and work-life referrals through the EAP. With some health insurance plans, you may be able to utilize your medical benefits for additional therapy visits. Check out your medical plan to see if this is offered."},{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"4LgioRRcQ8KAAaWYaW8AiW","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2018-10-24T20:33:16.676Z","updatedAt":"2020-06-16T23:13:17.645Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":4,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"sectionContent"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"Ext Global Section - Business Travel","sectionTitle":"Business Travel","sectionDescription":"Netflix provides benefits to protect your safety and security when traveling outside of the country you work. We offer both a travel concierge service through International SOS and