e ability to save for retirement, a choice in the degree to which they participate in equity investment, and the option to make an impact on a global level by participating in our Employee Giving Program."},{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"6tTPK0lS7uSgks2eca8SwI","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2018-10-25T21:06:37.957Z","updatedAt":"2020-12-28T21:12:49.393Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":3,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"sectionContent"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"Ext Global Section - Employee Giving","sectionTitle":"Employee Giving","sectionDescription":"At Netflix, you have the ability to impact the world through the work you do. And we realize you may also want to make an impact in a more personal way. In the spirit of freedom and responsibility, you choose the organization(s) important to you, and Netflix will match your contribution $2 dollars for every $1 you donate up to $20,000 (or local currency equivalent)."},{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"79hEZR4HmM0sjWipyohxrc","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2019-05-08T23:57:23.132Z","updatedAt":"2021-01-16T02:46:34.654Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":6,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"sectionGroup"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"Ext Mexico, Philippines, Brazil, Italy, Turkey Section Group - Stock Option Program (5% with supplemental)","title":"Stock Option Program (SOP)","content":[{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"ILVVvWgWAuUEyyuwqoOgM","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2018-10-31T20:26:07.647Z","updatedAt":"2021-01-15T17:22:26.544Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":5,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"sectionContent"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"SOP Philosophy","sectionTitle":"Philosophy","sectionDescription":"__The Why__\nThe Netflix Stock Option Program (SOP) is unique. At Netflix, we believe in top-of-personal-market pay and providing employees with a choice in the degree to which they invest in Netflix equity through the stock option program."},{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"1Pr9AeDAAfyFvD07WMHHBM","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2019-05-07T22:03:06.449Z","updatedAt":"2021-01-16T02:02:20.710Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":12,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"sectionContent"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"SOP - Overview (Pt 1 Internal and External Mexico, Brazil, Philippines, Italy)","sectionTitle":"Overview","sectionDescription":"## The Program\nYou have the opportunity to choose the amount of cash and equity you want to receive. The stock allocation is completely voluntary. If you’d like to receive options, you can allocate as much eligible salary to the SOP as you’d like. The program allows you to benefit from the growth of our stock price over time by accumulating options and then exercising them later when the price of the underlying Netflix stock has risen. \n\nFollowing your initial eligibility, you’ll be limited to maintaining or reducing your allocation during open enrollment for the next plan year, unless you receive a pay increase. In that instance you’ll be able to increase your allocation to an amount corresponding to the salary increase.\n\u003c/br\u003e\n## What is a stock option?\nA stock option is the right to purchase a share of Netflix stock at a predetermined price, called the exercise price. Options become valuable as the stock price appreciates above the exercise price. Netflix options are granted each month and expire 10 years from the grant date. \n\nA simple way to think of a stock option is to think of it like a coupon. The coupon is valuable to you when the regular price of the item is higher than what you can buy it for with your coupon, and once they expire they are longer valid. Let’s say you receive a coupon to buy an item at 100 until the printed expiration date. You go into the store and see that the retail price is 150. You redeem your coupon and buy it for 100, which saves you 50. In the context of stock options, you might have an option with an exercise price of 100. You exercise and sell your option later on when your stock price is 150, so your gain is 50!\n"},{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"nAKCdbZhkWaCgUUWe02S0","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2018-09-18T01:29:50.594Z","updatedAt":"2021-01-16T02:06:13.163Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":32,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"sectionContent"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"SOP \u003e Option Grants","sectionTitle":"Option Grants","sectionDescription":"Options are granted on the first trading day of each month. The exercise price of your options will be the closing price of Netflix stock on the day that the options are granted.\n\nGenerally, there are two factors that determine the number of options you receive: \n  1) the amount you are contributing to the program and \n  2) the cost of each option. \n\nWe calculate the monthly contribution by taking the annual amount that you’ve allocated and dividing it by twelve. The cost of each option is 40% of the exercise price. We’ll divide the monthly contribution by the cost of the option,  then we know how many options you should get for the month.\n\n![(5%) Your Annual Allocation / 12](//images.ctfassets.net/abx5xo923wy6/6nvGrFnyv7rtSH2OIT2EQE/40e04d877cb8c5bb47ca74762506c77f/_5-__Your_Annual_Allocation___12.png)\n\nAs an example, assume the following:\n- Your Annual Allocation: = $12,000 annually or $1,000 monthly\n- Closing Price on the Grant Day: $200\n\nMonthly Calculation:\n![(5% SOP) $1000 / 40% x $200](//images.ctfassets.net/abx5xo923wy6/Nc3FvMKTvwCAWZZbUYyhz/e3051ca4c9ef365725a8e3cd9a7450d7/_5-_SOP___1000___40-_x__200.png)\n\nNow you have 12 options or, in other words, the right to buy 12 shares of Netflix stock at $200.\n\nA couple of points not mentioned above for simplicity's sake:\n- We don’t grant fractional options so we always round down; any remaining amount of allocation is carried over to the next month.\n- When you first join your option allocation is prorated from your hire date.\n"},{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"6LaqHSUAG1Kh5vYR1SkzJA","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2020-08-07T22:28:07.301Z","updatedAt":"2021-01-15T17:23:31.911Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":3,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"sectionContent"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"SOP \u003e Vest Schedule","sectionTitle":"Vest Schedule","sectionDescription":"Good news! Our options are immediately vested. This means that we can exercise our options whenever we would like, subject to insider trading restrictions."},{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"6pSNAGyQz5bci6QUXxCvmz","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2020-08-07T22:29:51.846Z","updatedAt":"2021-01-15T17:23:54.048Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":3,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"sectionContent"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"SOP \u003e Option Expiration","sectionTitle":"Option Expiration","sectionDescription":"Generally, your options will expire 10 years after the grant date, regardless of your employment status."},{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"7cNJn2CgoeQFDsjyuh4Llz","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2021-01-15T19:10:51.128Z","updatedAt":"2021-01-15T22:05:32.553Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":2,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"sectionContent"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"Supplemental SOP \u003e Understanding the Value of Your Options","sectionTitle":"Understanding the Value of Your Options","sectionDescription":"Simply put, options gain value as the stock price appreciates above the exercise price. The higher the stock price goes above the exercise price, the more your options are worth.\nParticipating in the program is an investment choice that allows you to exchange salary for options. The salary you exchange goes to cover the cost of the options, which is 40% of the exercise price. You could consider  this as the premium you pay to get the right to buy a share at the exercise price. When thinking about the actual value of the options, you want to consider this 40% cost as your initial investment. \n\nIn our example above, we exchanged $80 of our salary to get each option with a $200 exercise price. If we have exchanged $80 of salary for each option to buy a share at $200, our total investment will be $280 per share.\n\nThe stock price would need to go up to at least $280 before we start to make a profit on the salary we exchanged, which means the stock value must appreciate by at least 40% above the exercise price. Continuing our example, let us assume that we exercise and sell our 5 options at $300. If we invested $280 per option and sold at $300, our profit is $20 per option, or $100 total***.\n\n![(5% SOP) (Sell Price - (Option Cost + Exercise Price)) * Number of Options](//images.ctfassets.net/abx5xo923wy6/7aoRJj75et1XNFknt1V0UI/402f86e62e2c17df64e863b1408ad8da/_5-_SOP___Sell_Price_-__Option_Cost___Exercise_Price_____Number_of_Options.png)\n\nThis doesn’t mean that you must wait until the stock price goes up at least 40% before you exercise however. You can exercise your options at any point, as long as the stock price is above the exercise price. \n\n***To keep the math simple, the above examples do not include taxes or fees."}]}]}]},{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"46w9gjDywoEgiWaQm48yM6","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2018-10-24T22:34:26.667Z","updatedAt":"2020-06-24T21:34:21.622Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":31,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"externalTab"}},"locale":"en-US"},"title":"Life Happens","locationBasedContent":[{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"7ciucSHsGIIeC8smCAuUa4","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2018-10-29T19:43:10.448Z","updatedAt":"2020-09-24T21:47:36.378Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":7,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"locationBasedContent"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"Ext US - Life Happens","location":{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"71tweP9sK440IwCGyUagK0","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2018-07-30T16:29:50.993Z","updatedAt":"2020-11-05T16:33:15.923Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":8,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"locationData"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"United States","locationName":"United States","flag":{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"3yIeCkVLluimeiYAqUWqEc","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2018-08-21T23:58:07.112Z","updatedAt":"2020-11-05T16:33:13.043Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":7,"locale":"en-US"},"title":"us","url":"//images.ctfassets.net/abx5xo923wy6/3yIeCkVLluimeiYAqUWqEc/c36f12a041ea74cdc04b947c8eca0042/us_flag.svg","details":{"size":6757,"image":{"width":28,"height":20}},"fileName":"us flag.svg","contentType":"image/svg+xml"},"slug":"united-states"},"locationSpecificContent":[{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"5Aoh1ebS7jybxWqX8Q71xi","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2020-09-24T21:47:29.052Z","updatedAt":"2020-09-24T21:47:29.052Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":1,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"sectionContent"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"Ext - Global - Life Happens Philosophy ","sectionTitle":"Philosophy","sectionDescription":"When it comes to your life, it’s not our place to decide what things you should care about. We believe in providing the resources that will alleviate distractions, take care of you and your family, and allow you to do your best work."},{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"2eHoDDUsvSKgqiowa60g2s","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2018-10-24T20:16:24.201Z","updatedAt":"2020-03-18T19:03:19.375Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":12,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"sectionContent"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"Ext Global Section - Leaves of Absence","sectionTitle":"Leaves of Absence","sectionDescription":"Whether you need time to care for a sick family member, to care for yourself or to bond with a new baby or child, Netflix offers generous paid time away for these priorities. We are here to support you during these times.\n\n\n## Parental Leave\nWelcoming a new child is one of the most special moments in a person’s life. We want you to be present and enjoy your growing family.\n\nIf you’re a salaried employee, you’ll receive 100% of your salary while you’re away from work to care and bond with your new child. You’ll work with your manager and business partner to determine the amount of time away. If you’re an hourly employee, you’ll receive 24 weeks of paid time off."},{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"4SQfaf0IxOAQUmUieWE4mq","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2018-10-30T17:37:46.985Z","updatedAt":"2018-11-14T20:08:35.312Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":2,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"sectionContent"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"Ext US Section - Disability","sectionDescription":"## Disability\nNetflix provides a combination of short and long term disability for serious injury or illness. Netflix will provide 100% of your pay for the first 12 weeks, and you’ll receive 70% of your pay for the remaining 40 weeks. If your injury or illness lasts longer than 52 weeks, you’ll become eligible for the LTD plan through Liberty. You’ll receive 70% of your pay (up to $20,000/month)."},{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"3z6NioZ0bm0owoQnYwqRHY","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2019-10-18T00:09:23.760Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-18T00:09:23.760Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":1,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"sectionContent"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"Ext US Section - Military","sectionDescription":"## Military\nNetflix provides 100% pay for the duration of your active duty and/or training."},{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"5fd0sOCQsEqyIEcIUOEiUI","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2019-01-08T23:44:54.713Z","updatedAt":"2019-06-11T20:13:09.470Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":2,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"sectionContent"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"Ext Global Section - Family Forming Header","sectionTitle":"Family Forming"},{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"3hi06oxzbi0iwgOKa8u4os","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2018-11-29T21:56:51.423Z","updatedAt":"2020-03-24T19:08:50.087Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":10,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"sectionContent"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"Family Forming Intro","sectionDescription":"Netflix offers a global family forming benefit to support you during your fertility, surrogacy, or adoption journey. This benefit is available to all full time, regular Streaming employees and their spouse/domestic partner, regardless of marital status, gender, or sexual orientation. We recognize these pathways are challenging from both a financial and emotional perspective. To support this journey, we have partnered with [Carrot](https://www.get-carrot.com/ \"Carrot\"), who will help provide guidance and support in order to remove distractions so that you can be more productive and focus on solving problems and doing great work at Netflix. Netflix also offers an allowance through Carrot to support you in covering the costs of your family forming journey.\n\n__Family Forming Covid-19 update:__ Carrot has provided a resource page to support employees through Covid-19 [here](https://www.get-carrot.com/covid-19?utm_source=email\u0026_hsenc=p2ANqtz-86lqHpFBTVXiXsYvBPq2eiVY-u0Yuze3hu8nXbdoaHGb2sTjUB07hgrOjCUdA_3-27eLSvJHs4uGARU8cNZ-QqZK_HGw\u0026_hsmi=85194432). "},{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"5wxIuLQ5H2o2au8ogGeKKG","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2018-10-30T17:29:22.892Z","updatedAt":"2020-09-14T20:42:49.519Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":5,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"sectionContent"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"Ext US - Family Care / Home Resources","sectionTitle":"Family Care / Home Resources","sectionDescription":"To help remove distractions from your life, Netflix pays for 10 days of child, elder, adult, or pet backup care through care.com. Services for your home and pets can also be be accessed through your free membership with care.com."},{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"4VtoxHNCog0qyikEkaQ88m","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2018-10-24T20:18:55.001Z","updatedAt":"2019-09-16T22:16:06.453Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":4,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"sectionContent"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"Ext US Section - Personal Legal / Financial Support","sectionTitle":"Personal Legal / Financial Support","sectionDescription":"We offer an EAP (Employee Assistance Program) — a free and confidential resource available to you and your dependents when you need a little help resolving life’s issues. It includes financial coaching and legal help."},{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"43YeNLeqIg0cIeIsqSog2m","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2018-10-24T20:22:06.207Z","updatedAt":"2019-09-16T22:16:26.550Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":8,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"sectionContent"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"Ext Global Section - Life and Serious Injury Benefit","sectionTitle":"Life and Serious Injury Benefit","sectionDescription":"In the unfortunate event that an employee passes away, Netflix provides a taxable $1.5 million USD Life benefit to the employee's designated beneficiary. The Life benefit provides financial protection for beneficiaries when an employee passes away. We're asked how this benefit came to be, and the answer is simple: When the need arose. After an employee working at Netflix passed away suddenly, Netflix provided a $1 million benefit (this increased to $1.5 million in 2018) to the family to help lessen their worry. That decision has since become Netflix practice. \n\n*[beneficiary]: The person, or estate, that is designated to receive benefits in the event of your death."}]},{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"63AfV8LDpKSIycc4cewsiW","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2018-10-26T19:48:22.888Z","updatedAt":"2020-09-24T21:47:42.541Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":5,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"locationBasedContent"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"Ext Brazil - Life Happens","location":{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"9AVxBQOFHiKocUi4SwAcs","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2018-08-17T17:46:02.079Z","updatedAt":"2020-11-05T16:33:14.913Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":7,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"locationData"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"Brazil","locationName":"Brazil","flag":{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"4s5CJ6vi0M44ks4m682iEA","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2018-08-22T16:50:13.763Z","updatedAt":"2020-11-05T16:33:13.009Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":5,"locale":"en-US"},"title":"BR","url":"//images.ctfassets.net/abx5xo923wy6/4s5CJ6vi0M44ks4m682iEA/57130703315a5b4c101a7782a0caa977/BR.svg","details":{"size":2372,"image":{"width":28,"height":20}},"fileName":"BR.svg","contentType":"image/svg+xml"},"slug":"brazil"},"locationSpecificContent":[{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"5Aoh1ebS7jybxWqX8Q71xi","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2020-09-24T21:47:29.052Z","updatedAt":"2020-09-24T21:47:29.052Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":1,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"sectionContent"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"Ext - Global - Life Happens Philosophy ","sectionTitle":"Philosophy","sectionDescription":"When it comes to your life, it’s not our place to decide what things you should care about. We believe in providing the resources that will alleviate distractions, take care of you and your family, and allow you to do your best work."},{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"2eHoDDUsvSKgqiowa60g2s","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2018-10-24T20:16:24.201Z","updatedAt":"2020-03-18T19:03:19.375Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":12,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"sectionContent"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"Ext Global Section - Leaves of Absence","sectionTitle":"Leaves of Absence","sectionDescription":"Whether you need time to care for a sick family member, to care for yourself or to bond with a new baby or child, Netflix offers generous paid time away for these priorities. We are here to support you during these times.\n\n\n## Parental Leave\nWelcoming a new child is one of the most special moments in a person’s life. We want you to be present and enjoy your growing family.\n\nIf you’re a salaried employee, you’ll receive 100% of your salary while you’re away from work to care and bond with your new child. You’ll work with your manager and business partner to determine the amount of time away. If you’re an hourly employee, you’ll receive 24 weeks of paid time off."},{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"5fd0sOCQsEqyIEcIUOEiUI","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2019-01-08T23:44:54.713Z","updatedAt":"2019-06-11T20:13:09.470Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":2,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"sectionContent"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"Ext Global Section - Family Forming Header","sectionTitle":"Family Forming"},{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"3hi06oxzbi0iwgOKa8u4os","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2018-11-29T21:56:51.423Z","updatedAt":"2020-03-24T19:08:50.087Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":10,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"sectionContent"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"Family Forming Intro","sectionDescription":"Netflix offers a global family forming benefit to support you during your fertility, surrogacy, or adoption journey. This benefit is available to all full time, regular Streaming employees and their spouse/domestic partner, regardless of marital status, gender, or sexual orientation. We recognize these pathways are challenging from both a financial and emotional perspective. To support this journey, we have partnered with [Carrot](https://www.get-carrot.com/ \"Carrot\"), who will help provide guidance and support in order to remove distractions so that you can be more productive and focus on solving problems and doing great work at Netflix. Netflix also offers an allowance through Carrot to support you in covering the costs of your family forming journey.\n\n__Family Forming Covid-19 update:__ Carrot has provided a resource page to support employees through Covid-19 [here](https://www.get-carrot.com/covid-19?utm_source=email\u0026_hsenc=p2ANqtz-86lqHpFBTVXiXsYvBPq2eiVY-u0Yuze3hu8nXbdoaHGb2sTjUB07hgrOjCUdA_3-27eLSvJHs4uGARU8cNZ-QqZK_HGw\u0026_hsmi=85194432). "},{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"7wIr6AdmZqwm4cEWyYmOyG","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2018-10-25T20:29:24.444Z","updatedAt":"2018-10-25T20:29:24.444Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":1,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"sectionContent"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"Ext Global Section - Personal Legal / Financial Support","sectionTitle":"Personal Legal / Financial Support","sectionDescription":"We offer an EAP (Employee Assistance Program) — a free and confidential resource available to you and your dependents when you need a little help resolving life’s issues. It includes financial coaching and legal help."},{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"Bx6Vp4NFAciw4GsqC2yyE","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2018-10-29T19:58:25.889Z","updatedAt":"2018-10-29T19:58:25.889Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":1,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"sectionContent"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"Ext Brazil Section - Disability","sectionTitle":"Disability","sectionDescription":"Netflix provides disability coverage to replace 100% of your income for up to three months if you are unable to work due to illness or injury. Netflix also covers 70% of your salary for 3–11 months if you are unable to work due to illness or injury. You also get Total \u0026 Permanent Disability coverage of two times your annual salary. You may also be eligible for state Social Security benefits (INSS). Your Netflix sick leave payment will be integrated with INSS benefit payments."},{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"43YeNLeqIg0cIeIsqSog2m","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2018-10-24T20:22:06.207Z","updatedAt":"2019-09-16T22:16:26.550Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":8,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"sectionContent"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"Ext Global Section - Life and Serious Injury Benefit","sectionTitle":"Life and Serious Injury Benefit","sectionDescription":"In the unfortunate event that an employee passes away, Netflix provides a taxable $1.5 million USD Life benefit to the employee's designated beneficiary. The Life benefit provides financial protection for beneficiaries when an employee passes away. We're asked how this benefit came to be, and the answer is simple: When the need arose. After an employee working at Netflix passed away suddenly, Netflix provided a $1 million benefit (this increased to $1.5 million in 2018) to the family to help lessen their worry. That decision has since become Netflix practice. \n\n*[beneficiary]: The person, or estate, that is designated to receive benefits in the event of your death."}]},{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"1bJrRFspmY8C4WeCw4YIse","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2018-10-26T21:12:32.596Z","updatedAt":"2020-09-24T21:47:49.333Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":7,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"locationBasedContent"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"Ext Belgium - Life Happens","location":{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"5rHzOkzSZqeOEIIGyUIq0y","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2018-08-17T17:45:50.738Z","updatedAt":"2020-11-05T16:33:15.384Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":7,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"locationData"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"Belgium","locationName":"Belgium","flag":{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"1BeDXojKKUQoGO2OGc6wms","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2018-08-22T16:49:18.069Z","updatedAt":"2020-11-05T16:33:13.021Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":5,"locale":"en-US"},"title":"BE","url":"//images.ctfassets.net/abx5xo923wy6/1BeDXojKKUQoGO2OGc6wms/87ec44ead0540329f3478e9e243a2217/BE.svg","details":{"size":1283,"image":{"width":28,"height":20}},"fileName":"BE.svg","contentType":"image/svg+xml"},"slug":"belgium"},"locationSpecificContent":[{"sys