kAqYKsGqC/60fcfbac15760e48914686a823da34dc/DE.svg","details":{"size":2717,"image":{"width":28,"height":20}},"fileName":"DE.svg","contentType":"image/svg+xml"},"slug":"germany"},"locationSpecificContent":[{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"5Aoh1ebS7jybxWqX8Q71xi","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2020-09-24T21:47:29.052Z","updatedAt":"2020-09-24T21:47:29.052Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":1,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"sectionContent"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"Ext - Global - Life Happens Philosophy ","sectionTitle":"Philosophy","sectionDescription":"When it comes to your life, it’s not our place to decide what things you should care about. We believe in providing the resources that will alleviate distractions, take care of you and your family, and allow you to do your best work."},{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"2eHoDDUsvSKgqiowa60g2s","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2018-10-24T20:16:24.201Z","updatedAt":"2020-03-18T19:03:19.375Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":12,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"sectionContent"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"Ext Global Section - Leaves of Absence","sectionTitle":"Leaves of Absence","sectionDescription":"Whether you need time to care for a sick family member, to care for yourself or to bond with a new baby or child, Netflix offers generous paid time away for these priorities. We are here to support you during these times.\n\n\n## Parental Leave\nWelcoming a new child is one of the most special moments in a person’s life. We want you to be present and enjoy your growing family.\n\nIf you’re a salaried employee, you’ll receive 100% of your salary while you’re away from work to care and bond with your new child. You’ll work with your manager and business partner to determine the amount of time away. If you’re an hourly employee, you’ll receive 24 weeks of paid time off."},{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"5fd0sOCQsEqyIEcIUOEiUI","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2019-01-08T23:44:54.713Z","updatedAt":"2019-06-11T20:13:09.470Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":2,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"sectionContent"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"Ext Global Section - Family Forming Header","sectionTitle":"Family Forming"},{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"3hi06oxzbi0iwgOKa8u4os","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2018-11-29T21:56:51.423Z","updatedAt":"2020-03-24T19:08:50.087Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":10,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"sectionContent"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"Family Forming Intro","sectionDescription":"Netflix offers a global family forming benefit to support you during your fertility, surrogacy, or adoption journey. This benefit is available to all full time, regular Streaming employees and their spouse/domestic partner, regardless of marital status, gender, or sexual orientation. We recognize these pathways are challenging from both a financial and emotional perspective. To support this journey, we have partnered with [Carrot](https://www.get-carrot.com/ \"Carrot\"), who will help provide guidance and support in order to remove distractions so that you can be more productive and focus on solving problems and doing great work at Netflix. Netflix also offers an allowance through Carrot to support you in covering the costs of your family forming journey.\n\n__Family Forming Covid-19 update:__ Carrot has provided a resource page to support employees through Covid-19 [here](https://www.get-carrot.com/covid-19?utm_source=email\u002