-US"},"cmsTitle":"Ext Global Section - Leaves of Absence","sectionTitle":"Leaves of Absence","sectionDescription":"Whether you need time to care for a sick family member, to care for yourself or to bond with a new baby or child, Netflix offers generous paid time away for these priorities. We are here to support you during these times.\n\n\n## Parental Leave\nWelcoming a new child is one of the most special moments in a person’s life. We want you to be present and enjoy your growing family.\n\nIf you’re a salaried employee, you’ll receive 100% of your salary while you’re away from work to care and bond with your new child. You’ll work with your manager and business partner to determine the amount of time away. If you’re an hourly employee, you’ll receive 24 weeks of paid time off."},{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"5fd0sOCQsEqyIEcIUOEiUI","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2019-01-08T23:44:54.713Z","updatedAt":"2019-06-11T20:13:09.470Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":2,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"sectionContent"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"Ext Global Section - Family Forming Header","sectionTitle":"Family Forming"},{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"3hi06oxzbi0iwgOKa8u4os","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2018-11-29T21:56:51.423Z","updatedAt":"2020-03-24T19:08:50.087Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":10,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"sectionContent"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"Family Forming Intro","sectionDescription":"Netflix offers a global family forming benefit to support you during your fertility, surrogacy, or adoption journey. This benefit is available to all full time, regular Streaming employees and their spouse/domestic partner, regardless of marital status, gender, or sexual