eat work at Netflix. Netflix also offers an allowance through Carrot to support you in covering the costs of your family forming journey.\n\n__Family Forming Covid-19 update:__ Carrot has provided a resource page to support employees through Covid-19 [here](https://www.get-carrot.com/covid-19?utm_source=email\u0026_hsenc=p2ANqtz-86lqHpFBTVXiXsYvBPq2eiVY-u0Yuze3hu8nXbdoaHGb2sTjUB07hgrOjCUdA_3-27eLSvJHs4uGARU8cNZ-QqZK_HGw\u0026_hsmi=85194432). "},{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"5hVmlG7WFUEow8WYyUowYS","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2018-10-25T19:57:24.006Z","updatedAt":"2020-09-14T20:40:11.513Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":4,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"sectionContent"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"Ext Section APAC - Family Care / Home Resources","sectionTitle":"Family Care / Home Resources","sectionDescription":"To help remove distractions from your life, our Employee Assistance Program provides services such as support for your child and elderly parents."},{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"7wIr6AdmZqwm4cEWyYmOyG","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2018-10-25T20:29:24.444Z","updatedAt":"2018-10-25T20:29:24.444Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":1,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"sectionContent"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"Ext Global Section - Personal Legal / Financial Support","sectionTitle":"Personal Legal / Financial Support","sectionDescription":"We offer an EAP (Employee Assistance Program) — a free and confidential resource available to you and your dependents when you need a little help resolving life’s issues. It includes financial coaching and legal help."},{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"vNqTWrGLFQCqeQe4wSKUg","type":"Entry