ome Resources","sectionDescription":"To help remove distractions from your life, Netflix pays for 10 days of child, elder, or adult backup care through [care.com](https://www.care.com/ \"care.com\"). Services for your home and pets can also be be accessed through your free membership with [care.com](https://www.care.com/ \"care.com\").  Similar services such as support for your child, elderly parents and home care also be found through the Employee Assistance Program."},{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"7wIr6AdmZqwm4cEWyYmOyG","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2018-10-25T20:29:24.444Z","updatedAt":"2018-10-25T20:29:24.444Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":1,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"sectionContent"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"Ext Global Section - Personal Legal / Financial Support","sectionTitle":"Personal Legal / Financial Support","sectionDescription":"We offer an EAP (Employee Assistance Program) — a free and confidential resource available to you and your dependents when you need a little help resolving life’s issues. It includes financial coaching and legal help."},{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"3cS8T5NbS0immgYKqiIIcs","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2018-10-29T20:20:44.611Z","updatedAt":"2018-10-29T20:20:44.611Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":1,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"sectionContent"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"Ext United Kingdom Section - Disability","sectionTitle":"Disability","sectionDescription":"Netflix provides disability coverage to replace 100% of your income for up to three months if you are unable to work due to illness or injury. Netflix also provides you with Long-Term Disability insurance to pick up where your sick leave ends if you’re sick or disabled for a longer period."},{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"43YeNLeqIg0cIeIsqSog2m","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2018-10-24T20:22:06.207Z","updatedAt":"2019-09-16T22:16:26.550Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":8,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"sectionContent"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"Ext Global Section - Life and Serious Injury Benefit","sectionTitle":"Life and Serious Injury Benefit","sectionDescription":"In the unfortunate event that an employee passes away, Netflix provides a taxable $1.5 million USD Life benefit to the employee's designated beneficiary. The Life benefit provides financial protection for beneficiaries when an employee passes away. We're asked how this benefit came to be, and the answer is simple: When the need arose. After an employee working at Netflix passed away suddenly, Netflix provided a $1 million benefit (this increased to $1.5 million in 2018) to the family to help lessen their worry. That decision has since become Netflix practice. \n\n*[beneficiary]: The person, or estate, that is designated to receive benefits in the event of your death."},{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"2AZjXrfcKuw7yaUigVx6Ce","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2020-09-28T12:30:59.500Z","updatedAt":"2020-09-28T12:30:59.500Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":1,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"sectionContent"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"Backup Care (Care@Work a service within Care.com)","sectionTitle":"Backup Care (Care@Work a service within Care.com)","sectionDescription":"Backup Care (Care@Work a service within Care.com)\nCare@Work also offers 10 days of backup child, elder, or adult care paid for by Netflix. The intention of backup care is to help you find a temporary, emergency or last minute caregiver in the case that your regular caregiver is not available, not to cover daily child care needs. Backup caregivers through Care@Work, which helps you get temporary care when you need it, are vetted and background checked by either Care.com or their network partners so that you can feel comfortable using them on short notice. No backup care options available? You also have the option to use your personal network for backup care. The Care@Work team does not perform a background check or vet these caregivers.\n\nExamples of when to use Backup Care:\n\nYour regular babysitter calls out sick, takes a personal day or is on vacation\nYou and/or your partner are sick and need extra support to watch your children\nYour partner had surgery and needs assistance around the house for a couple days\nYour childcare center has a power outage and is closed for the day"}]},{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"w09r8DFGYCEEQwOWi4wya","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2018-11-06T00:25:24.462Z","updatedAt":"2020-09-24T21:49:25.253Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":3,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"locationBasedContent"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"Ext France - Life Happens","location":{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"25TQNhqX4UWUg0KssIASoI","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2018-08-28T17:51:08.663Z","updatedAt":"2020-11-05T16:33:15.760Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":8,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"locationData"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"France","locationName":"France","flag":{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"6y7gVx4MqQEwemkWgkequI","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2018-08-28T18:03:20.383Z","updatedAt":"2020-11-05T16:33:13.036Z","environment":{"sys"