":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"2vF5favLyAaWAMAWcsa0UC","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2018-11-06T00:24:54.635Z","updatedAt":"2018-11-06T00:24:54.635Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":1,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"sectionContent"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"Ext France - Disability","sectionTitle":"Disabiliy","sectionDescription":"Netflix provides disability coverage to replace 100% of your income for up to three months if you are unable to work due to illness or injury. This will be integrated with any pay you receive from the government. \n\nAdditionally, Netflix provides a disability benefit through Allianz. After 90 days, the disability benefit and government coverage will cover 80% of your gross salary. The length of coverage depends on your sickness, accident, or injury. \n"},{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"43YeNLeqIg0cIeIsqSog2m","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2018-10-24T20:22:06.207Z","updatedAt":"2019-09-16T22:16:26.550Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":8,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"sectionContent"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"Ext Global Section - Life and Serious Injury Benefit","sectionTitle":"Life and Serious Injury Benefit","sectionDescription":"In the unfortunate event that an employee passes away, Netflix provides a taxable $1.5 million USD Life benefit to the employee's designated beneficiary. The Life benefit provides financial protection for beneficiaries when an employee passes away. We're asked how this benefit came to be, and the answer is simple: When the need arose. After an employee working at Netflix passed away suddenly, Netflix provided a $1 million benefit (this increased to $1.5 million in 2018) to the family to help lessen their worry. That decision has since become Netflix practice. \n\n*[be