e’s issues. It includes financial coaching and legal help."},{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"7uYaY1ALz3ZSJ3ayFxeQsM","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2020-06-17T03:07:16.139Z","updatedAt":"2020-06-17T03:07:16.139Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":1,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"sectionContent"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"Ext Turkey Section - Disability","sectionTitle":"Disability","sectionDescription":"Netflix provides disability coverage to replace 100% of your income for up to three months if you are unable to work due to illness or injury.  Once we reach 10 employees, we will implement an insured disability plan."},{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"43YeNLeqIg0cIeIsqSog2m","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2018-10-24T20:22:06.207Z","updatedAt":"2019-09-16T22:16:26.550Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":8,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"sectionContent"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"Ext Global Section - Life and Serious Injury Benefit","sectionTitle":"Life and Serious Injury Benefit","sectionDescription":"In the unfortunate event that an employee passes away, Netflix provides a taxable $1.5 million USD Life benefit to the employee's designated beneficiary. The Life benefit provides financial protection for beneficiaries when an employee passes away. We're asked how this benefit came to be, and the answer is simple: When the need arose. After an employee working at Netflix passed away suddenly, Netflix provided a $1 million benefit (this increased to $1.5 million in 2018) to the family to help lessen their worry. That decision has since become Netflix practice. \n\n*[beneficiary]: The person, or estate, that is designated to receive benefits in the event of your death."}]}]},{"sys":{"space"