 freedom and responsibility, giving you the power to choose when you need to take time off. When something’s being delivered or repaired, do what you need to do. When you’re sick, take the time to get better. The same goes if a child or partner is sick. Take care of them so your mind is clear and focused when you’re back at work. Just let others know where you are (we worry) and how you’re balancing work.\n\nIf you're a __salaried employee__, you have unlimited time off. When you need time away, just let others know where you are and how you're balancing work.\n\nIf you're a __full-time hourly employee__, you'll accrue 35 days per year (8.75 days per quarter). If you're a __part-time hourly employee__, you accrue 50% of the full-time rate. \n\n![1 Plan Centered Wide](//images.ctfassets.net/abx5xo923wy6/4VjSbKcnNemMUmAU4w6C6s/2adf22f54d07972e470492fc9c1aec68/1_Plan_Centered_Wide.png)"}]},{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"3HERhK3leEcYIiOiKgCgao","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2018-10-25T21:22:19.852Z","updatedAt":"2020-09-24T21:50:48.778Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":2,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"locationBasedContent"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"Ext Singapore - Work Not Drive","location":{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"3a6MzDvQ7KcuYouYYwMEC0","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2018-08-17T17:46:57.691Z","updatedAt":"2020-11-05T16:33:14.290Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":7,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"locationData"}},"locale":"en-US"},"cmsTitle":"Singapore","locationName":"Singapore","flag":{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"abx5xo923wy6"}},"id":"6cvLbm6iWW6QyKucYWYAQe","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2018-08-22T16:58:19.234Z","updatedAt":"2020-11-05T16:33:1